snippet.title: Test Drive (DOS, 1987)
snippet.description:
The MS-DOS version of Test Drive, played in EGA mode.

During my first game I get an immediate game over because I crash into a police car. Too bad, because I nearly passed the car in front of me and that might have gotten rid of him.

In the second game I make it to the gas station. Turns out I'm not that good at this game (actually, I just really like sightseeing).

I did better in this recording: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mz2cu8fpKtw
